WEBVTT

00:03.167 --> 00:04.333
PREVIOUSLY ON
"SINGLE LADIES"...

00:04.333 --> 00:05.567
HE'S MY PROFESSOR.

00:05.567 --> 00:07.100
LOOKS LIKE YOU WERE GETTING
SOME SERIOUS EXTRA CREDIT.

00:07.100 --> 00:09.000
IF HE DOESN'T FINISH AN ALBUM
IN TWO MONTHS,

00:09.000 --> 00:10.100
YOU'RE OUT THE DOOR WITH HIM.

00:10.100 --> 00:12.033
ARE YOU HIGH?
WHAT IS YOUR DEAL?

00:12.033 --> 00:15.533
I CAN'T RUSH INTO ANYTHING,
ESPECIALLY ANYTHING PHYSICAL.

00:15.533 --> 00:18.500
THIS IS THE SOUTH.
IT'S EASY TO GO SLOW.

00:21.600 --> 00:22.800
STEALING HIS WATCH HAS
BEEN ON MY CONSCIENCE

00:22.800 --> 00:24.533
EVER SINCE I TOOK IT.

00:24.533 --> 00:26.967
I THINK IT'S TIME
THAT I COME CLEAN WITH HIM.

00:26.967 --> 00:28.133
WELL, AS A MATTER OF FACT,
I DID.

00:28.133 --> 00:30.333
I SLEPT WITH
MY COLLEGE ROOMMATE VAL.

00:30.333 --> 00:31.867
[ GASPS ]
[ CLATTERS ]

00:31.867 --> 00:34.533
* SINGLE *
YEAH, YEAH.

00:34.533 --> 00:36.267
CAN YOU SAY LOVE CITY?

00:36.267 --> 00:38.467
* LADIES *

00:38.467 --> 00:40.133
CRAZY, CRAZY.

00:40.133 --> 00:42.167
* WHAT I WANT IS UP TO ME *

00:42.167 --> 00:44.167
* I CAN FOLLOW, I CAN LEAD *

00:44.167 --> 00:49.800
* LOSE CONTROL *

00:49.800 --> 00:51.533
* YOU CAN'T GET MY LOVE *

00:51.533 --> 00:55.100
* I KNOW YOU WANT IT *
* OH, YEAH *

00:55.100 --> 00:57.100
* YOU WANT IT *

00:57.100 --> 00:59.633
* SINGLE LADIES *

00:59.633 --> 01:01.833
WHERE MY SINGLE LADIES AT?

01:06.333 --> 01:09.100
MMM.

01:09.100 --> 01:11.800
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

01:16.633 --> 01:18.500
JERRY, THANK YOU AGAIN.

01:18.500 --> 01:20.467
I HAD SO MUCH FUN WITH YOU
THIS WEEKEND.

01:20.467 --> 01:23.267
TRUST ME,
I NEEDED TO GET AWAY.

01:23.267 --> 01:27.233
DARLING, ANY TIME YOU NEED
TO GET AWAY, EVEN WITHOUT ME,

01:27.233 --> 01:29.433
YOU ARE CARTE BLANCHE
ON MY JET.

01:29.433 --> 01:30.733
OKAY, JUST LET ME KNOW.

01:30.733 --> 01:32.667
I KEEP WAITING
FOR SOMEONE TO PINCH ME

01:32.667 --> 01:35.367
AND TELL ME THAT YOU ARE
JUST A DREAM.

01:35.367 --> 01:36.900
I PROMISE YOU I'M REAL,

01:36.900 --> 01:39.233
AS WAS LAS VEGAS.

01:39.233 --> 01:41.767
THANK YOU FOR TRUSTING ME ENOUGH
TO GO AWAY WITH ME THIS WEEKEND.

01:41.767 --> 01:45.700
NO. THANK YOU FOR BEING
A COMPLETE GENTLEMAN.

01:45.700 --> 01:48.667
IT'S RARE FOR ME TO MEET
A WOMAN THESE DAYS

01:48.667 --> 01:50.833
WHO WANTS TO TAKE THE TIME
TO GET TO KNOW A MAN.

01:50.833 --> 01:52.833
I RESPECT YOU FOR THAT.

01:52.833 --> 01:55.467
I ALSO RESPECT THE FACT
THAT IT'S 3:00 A.M.

01:55.467 --> 01:57.800
MM.
AND I'M GONNA CONTINUE
TO BE A GENTLEMAN

01:57.800 --> 02:00.067
AND LET YOU GET SOME SLEEP.
SO...

02:05.433 --> 02:07.533
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]
I'LL CALL YOU TOMORROW.

02:07.533 --> 02:09.400
I CAN ONLY HOPE.

02:13.067 --> 02:14.933
GOOD NIGHT.
GOOD NIGHT.

02:16.733 --> 02:17.933
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

02:20.867 --> 02:23.900
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

02:28.433 --> 02:30.667
[ Lowered voice ] VAL.

02:30.667 --> 02:32.467
MM.

02:32.467 --> 02:33.633
YOU UP?

02:33.633 --> 02:35.333
[ WHINES ]

02:35.333 --> 02:38.500
I AM NOW.

02:38.500 --> 02:40.900
DID YOU HAVE FUN IN VEGAS?

02:40.900 --> 02:43.900
[Whispers ]
I HAD THE BEST TIME.

02:43.900 --> 02:45.067
[Whispers ] OHH.

02:45.067 --> 02:46.700
JERRY HAS
A BEAUTIFUL HOUSE THERE.

02:46.700 --> 02:49.867
HE COOKED FOR ME
ALL WEEKEND LONG.

02:49.867 --> 02:51.633
HE TREATED ME LIKE A QUEEN.

02:51.633 --> 02:54.433
[ LAUGHS ]
AND TO TOP IT OFF...

02:54.433 --> 02:56.967
[Whispers ] WE SLEPT
IN SEPARATE BEDROOMS.

02:56.967 --> 02:58.433
MM-HMM.

02:58.433 --> 03:00.500
THE MAN IS CLASSY.
WOW.

03:00.500 --> 03:02.700
I'M READY GLAD
YOU HAD A GOOD TIME

03:02.700 --> 03:04.633
AND THAT YOU'RE IN
A GOOD PLACE.
MM-HMM.

03:04.633 --> 03:06.467
BECAUSE WHILE YOU WERE GONE...
HMM?

03:06.467 --> 03:09.133
THERE WERE SOME...
DEVELOPMENTS.

03:09.133 --> 03:11.667
WHAT KIND?

03:11.667 --> 03:13.067
MM.

03:19.100 --> 03:20.767
[ GASPS ]

03:20.767 --> 03:22.700
NO WAY! [ GASPS ]

03:22.700 --> 03:23.867
OH, MY GOD!

03:23.867 --> 03:25.633
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

03:25.633 --> 03:26.800
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

03:26.800 --> 03:28.833
HOW DID THEY TRACE THIS
BACK TO ME?!

03:28.833 --> 03:31.067
THERE ARE A MILLION VALS
IN THE WORLD.

03:31.067 --> 03:32.667
SHE COULD'VE BEEN TALKING
ABOUT ANYONE.

03:32.667 --> 03:34.833
YEAH, WELL, SHE WASN'T.

03:34.833 --> 03:37.867
REMEMBER NOW,
YOU'RE IN A GOOD PLACE.

03:37.867 --> 03:40.333
RIGHT. W-WHERE DID YOU
GET THAT FROM?

03:40.333 --> 03:42.200
WE JUST HAVE TO CALL
THE WEB SITE AND WE TELL THEM

03:42.200 --> 03:43.967
THEY HAVE TO TAKE IT DOWN
GOOD LUCK,

03:43.967 --> 03:45.867
BECAUSE IT'S ON GOOGLE

03:45.867 --> 03:47.367
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

03:47.367 --> 03:51.067
THESE PICTURES, THEY HAVE
ALL BEEN PHOTOSHOPPED.

03:51.067 --> 03:54.433
I HAVEN'T SPOKEN TO
OR SEEN SHARON IN YEARS.

03:54.433 --> 03:56.367
OKAY, FIRST THINGS FIRST --

03:56.367 --> 03:57.800
IS IT TRUE?

03:57.800 --> 04:01.333
DID YOU DO THE DIRTY DIRTY
WITH SHARON LOVE?

04:01.333 --> 04:02.667
KINDA.

04:02.667 --> 04:03.833
[ GASPS ]

04:03.833 --> 04:05.167
I MEAN, A LITTLE.
OOH-HOO!

04:05.167 --> 04:07.667
YES. BUT IT WAS JUST ONE TIME.

04:07.667 --> 04:10.967
WE WERE IN COLLEGE,
AND WE WERE BOTH DRUNK.

04:12.233 --> 04:13.833
IT JUST...HAPPENED.

04:15.367 --> 04:16.867
[ GASPS ] OH, MY GOD.

04:16.867 --> 04:18.567
[ GASPING ]

04:18.567 --> 04:21.333
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
WHAT AM I GONNA TELL MY MOTHER?

04:21.333 --> 04:23.067
JUST TELL HER THE TRUTH --

04:23.067 --> 04:24.267
YOU'RE GAY.

04:24.267 --> 04:26.100
OH, MY GOD.

04:26.100 --> 04:27.967
[ STIFLES LAUGH ]

04:31.267 --> 04:34.567
***

04:34.567 --> 04:37.600
[ WOMEN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

04:42.167 --> 04:44.867
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ] REED.

04:44.867 --> 04:46.533
REED.
WHAT?

04:46.533 --> 04:48.633
OH, APRIL. HEY.

04:48.633 --> 04:51.233
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE
ALL NIGHT?

04:51.233 --> 04:52.233
WHAT TIME IS IT?

04:52.233 --> 04:53.333
9:00.

04:53.333 --> 04:54.433
IN THE MORNING?

04:54.433 --> 04:56.167
WE'RE SUPPOSED
TO JUST TAKE A NAP.

04:56.167 --> 04:58.533
I SET MY PHONE.

04:58.533 --> 05:00.133
WHERE'S MY PHONE?

05:01.200 --> 05:03.500
[Whispers ] DAMN.
DID YOU GET ANY WORK DONE?

05:03.500 --> 05:04.767
DID YOU WORK
ON THAT NEW SONG?

05:04.767 --> 05:06.467
I STARTED TO, BUT I DON'T KNOW.
I WASN'T FEELING IT,

05:06.467 --> 05:09.233
SO I CALLED A COUPLE CHICKS OVER
HERE TO HELP ME GET MOTIVATED.

05:09.233 --> 05:10.667
THAT DIDN'T ANSWER
MY QUESTION.

05:10.667 --> 05:12.167
NO, APRIL, I DIDN'T.

05:12.167 --> 05:13.833
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]
IT'S NOT THE END OF THE WORLD.

05:13.833 --> 05:16.367
OH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
THE WORD IS SAFE.

05:16.367 --> 05:17.933
I'M JUST NOT SO SURE
ABOUT YOUR CAREER.

05:17.933 --> 05:20.700
IF YOU COULD FOCUS
FOR A COUPLE OF MONTHS,

05:20.700 --> 05:22.400
STOP PARTYING AND DRINKING
LONG ENOUGH

05:22.400 --> 05:25.333
TO FINISH YOUR DEBUT ALBUM,
YOU MIGHT ACTUALLY DEBUT.

05:25.333 --> 05:27.633
I -- THEN, YOU KNOW, STOP
PUTTING ME WITH THESE PRODUCERS

05:27.633 --> 05:28.933
THAT DON'T GET ME.

05:28.933 --> 05:31.467
PUT ME WITH HIT MAKERS
LIKE TIMBALAND OR PHARRELL,

05:31.467 --> 05:33.767
RODNEY JERKINS --
HELL, EVEN MAX MARTIN.

05:33.767 --> 05:36.767
I AGREE. YOU SHOULD BE WORKING
WITH SOME OF THE BEST PRODUCERS,

05:36.767 --> 05:37.933
BUT THEY'RE EXPENSIVE.

05:37.933 --> 05:39.100
AND YOU'VE ALREADY
BLOWN THROUGH THE MONEY

05:39.100 --> 05:40.367
THAT WES GAVE YOU UP FRONT.

05:40.367 --> 05:42.767
SO WE'RE KINDA WORKING ON FAVORS
RIGHT NOW, YOU KNOW?

05:42.767 --> 05:44.700
I'M TRYING TO PULL OUT
A MIRACLE.
WES LISTENS TO YOU.

05:44.700 --> 05:46.233
MAYBE YOU CAN GET HIM TO RELEASE
SOME OF THE MONEY

05:46.233 --> 05:48.400
I GET ON THE BACK END?
I TRIED THAT,

05:48.400 --> 05:50.433
AND THE STAPLER HE THREW AT ME
IS STILL STUCK IN THE WALL.

05:50.433 --> 05:51.600
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

05:51.600 --> 05:54.100
OH. [ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

05:56.600 --> 05:58.133
OKAY.

06:00.167 --> 06:02.333
I'M ABOUT TO DO SOMETHING
THAT'S GOING TO TURN OUT TO BE

06:02.333 --> 06:05.367
EITHER REALLY STUPID
OR ABSOLUTELY BRILLIANT.

06:05.367 --> 06:06.567
WHAT?

06:06.567 --> 06:09.133
I HAVE A LITTLE MONEY OF OWN

06:09.133 --> 06:11.067
THAT I'M WILLING TO INVEST
IN YOU.

06:11.067 --> 06:12.533
IF I GET YOU
A HEAVYWEIGHT PRODUCER,

06:12.533 --> 06:14.867
YOU HAVE TO PROMISE
YOU WON'T SCREW ME.

06:14.867 --> 06:16.667
[ SIGHS ]

06:16.667 --> 06:17.833
REED, LOOK AT ME.

06:17.833 --> 06:20.200
I AM SERIOUS.

06:20.200 --> 06:21.467
YOU'D DO THAT FOR ME?

06:21.467 --> 06:24.233
WE'VE ALREADY GONE OVER THIS.
IT'S FOR ME.

06:24.233 --> 06:25.467
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:28.733 --> 06:30.667
[ GRUNTS ]
I LOVE YOU.

06:33.400 --> 06:35.267
GET TO WORK.

06:39.967 --> 06:42.300
Omar: OKAY, WHAT ABOUT
ANGELINA JOLIE?

06:42.300 --> 06:43.600
I KNOW SHE'S TINY,

06:43.600 --> 06:45.500
BUT THOSE BIG, SEXY
EYES AND LIPS MAKE UP FOR IT.

06:45.500 --> 06:47.167
NAOMI CAMPBELL'S PRETTY.

06:47.167 --> 06:49.833
OR WHAT ABOUT CARMEN ELECTRA?
SHE'S STILL HOT.

06:49.833 --> 06:52.967
SALMA HAYEK? JLo?

06:52.967 --> 06:55.700
COME ON, VAL. WE'RE JUST TRYING
TO GET A FEEL FOR YOUR TASTE.

06:55.700 --> 06:58.200
I LIKE MEN.

06:58.200 --> 06:59.367
IT'S HALLE, AIN'T IT?

06:59.367 --> 07:00.600
I DON'T BLAME YOU.
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS ]

07:00.600 --> 07:02.133
HALLE'S FINE.
SHE COULD GET IT.

07:02.133 --> 07:03.233
ALL OF IT.

07:03.233 --> 07:05.800
YOU GUYS MUST NOT LIKE
BEING EMPLOYED,

07:05.800 --> 07:07.600
BECAUSE YOU'RE REALLY POKING
THE TIGER.

07:07.600 --> 07:09.100
VAL, FOR THE RECORD,

07:09.100 --> 07:12.633
I THINK YOU AND EVA LONGORIA
WOULD MAKE A CUTE COUPLE.

07:12.633 --> 07:13.867
THIS IS NUTS.
[ SHUTS CELL PHONE ]

07:13.867 --> 07:15.067
DO YOU KNOW HOW MANY
PHONE CALLS I'M GETTING

07:15.067 --> 07:17.200
FROM OLD FRIENDS
AND FAMILY MEMBERS,

07:17.200 --> 07:18.533
SAYING THAT THEY ALREADY KNEW,

07:18.533 --> 07:21.600
AND IT'S ABOUT TIME
THAT I CAME OUT OF THE CLOSET?

07:21.600 --> 07:23.433
Val: [ LAUGHS ]
WELL, YOU ARE IN YOUR 30s.

07:23.433 --> 07:25.433
YOU'RE STILL SINGLE.
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN MARRIED.

07:25.433 --> 07:27.433
YOU ALSO DON'T HAVE
ANY KIDS.
AND DON'T FORGET --

07:27.433 --> 07:29.233
YOU LIVE WITH A BEAUTIFUL,
VOLUPTUOUS WOMAN.

07:29.233 --> 07:30.533
Omar: WHO'S ALSO SINGLE.

07:30.533 --> 07:32.233
AND WHO ALSO
DOESN'T HAVE KIDS.

07:32.233 --> 07:34.300
HUH.

07:34.300 --> 07:36.200
I DO HAVE A GAY-LOOKING LIFE.

07:36.200 --> 07:38.167
IF I WERE GAY,
I WOULD JUST SAY SO.

07:38.167 --> 07:40.233
I MEAN, WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

07:40.233 --> 07:42.900
I HAD THAT SAME REVELATION
THREE DAYS AGO.

07:42.900 --> 07:46.467
HEY, VAL. HOW LONG HAS IT BEEN?
TEN YEARS?

07:46.467 --> 07:49.600
I DON'T KNOW WHETHER
TO STRANGLE YOU OR HUG YOU.

07:49.600 --> 07:51.400
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING,

07:51.400 --> 07:53.467
SAYING MY NAME ON THE AIR
LIKE THAT?

07:53.467 --> 07:55.367
I WAS THINKING
MY MIC WAS OFF.

07:55.367 --> 07:58.067
GIRL, I'VE BEEN TRYING
TO FIND YOU EVER SINCE,

07:58.067 --> 08:00.067
BUT I LOST YOUR NUMBER
THREE PHONES AGO.

08:00.067 --> 08:01.867
I'M SO SORRY.

08:01.867 --> 08:03.067
ANYWAY, THIS WHOLE THING
HAS BEEN A NIGHTMARE

08:03.067 --> 08:04.433
FOR THE BOTH OF US.
[ SCOFFS ]

08:04.433 --> 08:06.067
FOR ME, THE TIMING
COULDN'T BE WORSE.

08:06.067 --> 08:08.200
I JUST GOT MY OWN
NATIONAL TALK SHOW.

08:08.200 --> 08:10.500
CONGRATULATIONS!
THAT'S GREAT!

08:10.500 --> 08:13.100
YEAH, IT WAS GREAT UNTIL THIS
WHOLE THING SCARED CORPORATE.

08:13.100 --> 08:15.167
THEY A BUNCH
OF CONSERVATIVE OLD GUYS

08:15.167 --> 08:16.400
WHO ARE GIVING ME THE BLUES

08:16.400 --> 08:18.800
BECAUSE THEY DIDN'T BUY
A "GAY SHARON LOVE."

08:18.800 --> 08:22.067
THEY DON'T WANT
ANY CONTROVERSY.

08:22.067 --> 08:24.133
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

08:24.133 --> 08:26.067
EXCUSE ME, VAL.

08:26.067 --> 08:28.833
WOULD YOU LIKE TO JOIN US,
SINCE YOU'RE LISTENING ANYWAY?

08:28.833 --> 08:30.933
MNH-MNH.
UM...

08:30.933 --> 08:34.067
I'M HAPPY YOU GOT
YOUR OWN TALK SHOW,

08:34.067 --> 08:35.200
BECAUSE I WAS WORRIED ABOUT
WHAT I WAS GONNA DO

08:35.200 --> 08:37.267
WITH MY AFTERNOONS
ONCE "OPRAH" ENDED.

08:37.267 --> 08:39.867
BUT YOU THE PERFECT PERSON
TO FILL THAT VOID.

08:39.867 --> 08:42.067
AND THAT'S EXACTLY HOW
I SOLD IT.

08:42.067 --> 08:45.933
I SAID, "AMERICA IS GONNA NEED
ANOTHER BIG-BONED BLACK WOMAN

08:45.933 --> 08:48.700
WITH AMPLE BOSOM TO CRY INTO,
AND THAT'S ME."

08:48.700 --> 08:50.700
Val and Sharon: [ LAUGH ]

08:50.700 --> 08:53.167
I DON'T SEE IT.
I'M JUST KEEPING IT REAL.

08:53.167 --> 08:57.067
YOU HAVE A LOCAL APPEAL,
BUT NATIONAL?

08:57.067 --> 08:58.933
REALLY, GIRL? YOU?

08:58.933 --> 09:01.867
NAH. [ LAUGHS ]

09:01.867 --> 09:03.567
SINCE SHE HAS
THE GIFT OF FORESIGHT,

09:03.567 --> 09:05.300
I'M WONDERING WHY
SHE DIDN'T FORESEE

09:05.300 --> 09:06.667
THAT COLLEGE MIGHT'VE
SAVED HER

09:06.667 --> 09:09.200
FROM A LIFETIME
OF FOLDING SWEATERS.

09:09.200 --> 09:10.467
OH?
KEISHA.

09:10.467 --> 09:13.700
COULD YOU HELP THAT CUSTOMER
OVER THERE? PLEASE?

09:13.700 --> 09:15.900
VAL, YOU COULD'VE DONE BETTER,

09:15.900 --> 09:17.167
EVEN DRUNK.

09:18.567 --> 09:20.767
YOU KNOW, I'M DOING A SEGMENT
ON MY SHOW

09:20.767 --> 09:22.933
ABOUT WOMEN STRUGGLING
TO MAKE THE TRANSITION

09:22.933 --> 09:24.267
TO THE MAINSTREAM.

09:24.267 --> 09:27.200
JUST HOW LONG
HAS SHE BEEN OFF THE POLE?

09:27.200 --> 09:28.633
OH, LET ME TELL YA.
KEISHA, PLEASE.

09:28.633 --> 09:30.433
I KNOW A STRIPPER
WHEN I SEE ONE.

09:30.433 --> 09:31.600
Val: PLEASE.

09:31.600 --> 09:33.867
UM, I KNOW THIS IS
REALLY BAD TIMING,

09:33.867 --> 09:35.233
BUT MY MOM LOVES YOU,

09:35.233 --> 09:37.867
AND SHE WOULD KILL ME IF
I DIDN'T GET YOUR AUTOGRAPH.

09:37.867 --> 09:39.067
HERE YOU GO.

09:39.067 --> 09:40.600
AM I PUSHING IT?

09:40.600 --> 09:42.067
PICTURE?
[ LAUGHS ]

09:42.067 --> 09:44.200
GIRL, GIVE ME THE PHONE.
LET ME FIND MY LIGHT.

09:46.167 --> 09:48.067
YEAH, THAT'S GOOD.
CHEERS.

09:48.067 --> 09:49.100
***

09:49.100 --> 09:50.767
HEY, VAL, I SHOULD GO.

09:50.767 --> 09:53.567
I'M SURE THAT THIS WHOLE THING
IS GONNA BLOW OVER,

09:53.567 --> 09:54.867
ONCE CHARLIE SHEEN

09:54.867 --> 09:57.700
OR ONE OF THEM HOUSEWIVES
DOES SOMETHING STUPID.

09:57.700 --> 09:58.933
[ LAUGHS ] RIGHT?

09:58.933 --> 10:01.667
GIRL, YOU SHEDDIN'.

10:01.667 --> 10:03.033
OH. REALLY?

10:03.033 --> 10:05.400
YOU KNOW WHAT? WE HAD THOSE
WOOLS SWEATERS OVER THERE.

10:05.400 --> 10:07.233
OH, YOU GOT SOME
DOWN HERE, TOO.
DO I?

10:07.233 --> 10:08.567
THANK YOU. OH.
LOOK AT THAT.

10:08.567 --> 10:10.200
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]
OOH!

10:10.200 --> 10:11.833
Both: [ GASP ]
THANKS!

10:11.833 --> 10:14.333
THAT'LL BE WORTH
AT LEAST $2,500.

10:14.333 --> 10:15.767
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:15.767 --> 10:17.067
THANK YOU!

10:19.800 --> 10:22.467
SHARON!

10:22.467 --> 10:25.000
SHARON?!
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

10:25.000 --> 10:28.000
SHE PROBABLY LET THEM
IN HERE.

10:30.267 --> 10:31.600
Man: WITH A RIGHT HAND,
FINDS IT...

10:31.600 --> 10:33.667
[ LAUGHS ] OH!
[ GRUNTS ]

10:33.667 --> 10:35.300
UHH!
OH!

10:35.300 --> 10:37.367
YEAH!
YOU KNOCKED ME OUT!

10:37.367 --> 10:38.933
I THOUGHT YOU SAID YOU WERE
A SOUTHERN GENTLEMAN.

10:38.933 --> 10:40.967
HEY, NOT IN A BOXING RING,
SUGAR.

10:40.967 --> 10:42.600
OOH!
[ LAUGHS ]

10:42.600 --> 10:44.667
OH! [ SIGHS ] THAT WAS
QUITE A WORKOUT.

10:44.667 --> 10:47.333
I'M GONNA HAVE TO REHYDRATE
BEFORE OUR REMATCH.

10:47.333 --> 10:49.133
YEAH. [ SIGHS ]

10:49.133 --> 10:50.700
[Whispers ] WOW.

10:50.700 --> 10:53.333
WELL, NOW THAT
I BEAT UP ON YOU,

10:53.333 --> 10:57.133
CAN WE TALK ABOUT THE, UM,
ELEPHANT IN THE ROOM?

10:57.133 --> 10:58.533
[ GASPS ] OH.

10:58.533 --> 11:00.067
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:00.067 --> 11:01.300
OKAY. [ SIGHS ]

11:01.300 --> 11:04.200
YOU KNOW, I WAS HOPING
THIS WHOLE THING WOULD GO AWAY.

11:04.200 --> 11:06.200
MM-HMM.
YOU KNOW...

11:07.400 --> 11:09.233
IT WAS JUST ONE TIME
IN COLLEGE.

11:09.233 --> 11:11.767
I-I WAS TALKING ABOUT QUINN,

11:11.767 --> 11:15.067
BUT I DO WANNA GET BACK
TO THAT OTHER THING.

11:15.067 --> 11:16.733
OKAY.
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

11:16.733 --> 11:18.867
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ] SO WHAT
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW ABOUT QUINN?

11:18.867 --> 11:21.733
SWEETHEART, WHO YOU DATED --
THAT'S YOUR BUSINESS.

11:21.733 --> 11:24.067
BUT QUINN WAS ENGAGED
TO MY DAUGHTER,

11:24.067 --> 11:25.533
AND I HAPPEN TO OWN
THE TEAM HE PLAYS FOR,

11:25.533 --> 11:26.700
SO I JUST WANNA MAKE SURE

11:26.700 --> 11:28.600
THAT YOU'RE NOT UNCOMFORTABLE
WITH THAT.

11:28.600 --> 11:30.067
THAT'S SWEET OF YOU TO ASK.

11:30.067 --> 11:32.633
I DIDN'T BRING IT UP
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T BRING IT UP.

11:32.633 --> 11:34.367
I WOULD SAY SO IF IT DID.

11:34.367 --> 11:38.733
TRUST ME. QUINN IS
THE FURTHEST THING FROM MY MIND.

11:38.733 --> 11:41.867
WHY? DOES IT MAKE YOU
UNCOMFORTABLE?

11:41.867 --> 11:45.067
I'M HERE, AIN'T I?

11:50.267 --> 11:53.400
SO NOW THAT
THAT'S OUT OF THE WAY...

11:53.400 --> 11:55.867
YOU WANNA KNOW
ABOUT SHARON LOVE.

11:55.867 --> 11:57.067
MM-HMM.

11:57.067 --> 11:58.533
NO, WE ARE NOT A COUPLE,

11:58.533 --> 12:01.233
AND NO, I AM NOT A LESBIAN.

12:01.233 --> 12:03.167
OKAY.

12:03.167 --> 12:04.300
[ SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE ]
OKAY.

12:04.300 --> 12:05.533
I HAVE TO ADMIT THAT

12:05.533 --> 12:06.767
THE REASON I THOUGHT
YOU WERE TAKING IT SLOW

12:06.767 --> 12:09.167
WAS THAT I WAS JUST A BEARD.

12:09.167 --> 12:10.667
YOU SERIOUSLY THOUGHT THAT?

12:10.667 --> 12:12.967
COME ON, THIS IS ATLANTA.
IT'S A GREAT CITY,

12:12.967 --> 12:16.167
BUT NOT EVERYBODY IS AS EVOLVED
AS YOU WANT THEM TO BE.

12:16.167 --> 12:17.767
A LOT OF SOCIAL PRESSURE
ON A WOMAN

12:17.767 --> 12:20.100
TO HAVE A MAN,
HAVE A FAMILY.

12:20.100 --> 12:23.133
JERRY, PLEASE.
[ CHUCKLES ] STOP.

12:23.133 --> 12:27.067
I LIKE MEN.
IN FACT, I LOVE MEN.

12:27.067 --> 12:30.400
AND THE REASON I TAKE IT SLOW
IS BECAUSE IN THE PAST,

12:30.400 --> 12:33.800
I HAVE ALWAYS BEEN TOO QUICK
TO JUMP IN WITH BOTH FEET

12:33.800 --> 12:34.967
WITHOUT TAKING THE TIME

12:34.967 --> 12:37.733
TO MAKE SURE THAT
THE RELATIONSHIP IS RIGHT.

12:37.733 --> 12:38.900
[ MOUTHS WORD ]

12:38.900 --> 12:43.067
I TAKE IT SLOW
BECAUSE WHEN YOU WAIT,

12:43.067 --> 12:45.467
IT MAKES IT
ALL THE MORE SPECIAL.

12:45.467 --> 12:48.933
OKAY. I STAND CORRECTED.

12:48.933 --> 12:52.100
YOU SERIOUSLY THOUGHT
I WAS USING YOU AS A BEARD?

12:52.100 --> 12:53.333
[ LAUGHS ]

12:53.333 --> 12:54.933
PUT YOUR GLOVES ON.

12:57.467 --> 13:00.167
ORDINARILY,
I DON'T HIT WOMEN.

13:00.167 --> 13:01.367
OH.

13:03.067 --> 13:04.700
[ BOXING RING BELL DINGS ]
[ LAUGHS ]

13:04.700 --> 13:06.667
[ MAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

13:06.667 --> 13:10.967
***

13:10.967 --> 13:13.667
YOU SURE YOU DON'T NEED ME
TO STAY, VAL?

13:13.667 --> 13:15.733
WE COULD GET
A RUSH OF CUSTOMERS ANY MINUTE.

13:15.733 --> 13:18.300
NO, YOU CAN GO.

13:18.300 --> 13:20.233
SLOW DAY.
KEISHA AND I CAN HANDLE IT.

13:20.233 --> 13:21.667
ALL RIGHT.
[ AIR KISSES ]

13:25.500 --> 13:26.900
QUIT PLAYIN'.

13:26.900 --> 13:29.600
I WAS TRYING TO SEE IF I PASSED
MY REAL ESTATE LICENSE EXAM.

13:31.133 --> 13:32.633
KEISHA.
[Whispers ] WHAT?

13:32.633 --> 13:35.100
IT WAS A TEST.
OF COURSE YOU DIDN'T PASS.

13:36.667 --> 13:39.633
YOU MIGHT WANNA BUTCH UP
YOUR RUN.

13:43.067 --> 13:44.333
[ GASPS ]

13:44.333 --> 13:46.933
WHAT HAPPENED?
DID YOU PASS?

13:46.933 --> 13:49.867
YEAH. [ LAUGHING ]
[ SQUEALS ]

13:49.867 --> 13:51.333
I KNEW I WANTED
TO GET MY LICENSE,

13:51.333 --> 13:53.567
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW
IT WOULD FEEL THIS GOOD.

13:53.567 --> 13:56.733
I MEAN, I STILL NEED TO GET
A BROKER TO SPONSOR ME, BUT...

13:56.733 --> 13:59.067
I PASSED! [ LAUGHS ]
[ LAUGHS ]

13:59.067 --> 14:00.633
OH, CONGRATULATIONS.

14:00.633 --> 14:01.800
I AM SO PROUD OF YOU,
KEISH.

14:01.800 --> 14:03.633
MMM. THANKS.

14:03.633 --> 14:06.367
ME, TOO. MMM, MMM, MMM.

14:06.367 --> 14:08.200
DON'T LET ME GET INTERESTED
IN MEDICINE.

14:08.200 --> 14:11.433
