AND VAL REALLY NEEDS ME TO STAY,

14:20.067 --> 14:22.600
SO I'M GONNA HAVE TO RESCHEDULE
OUR LUNCH TODAY.

14:22.600 --> 14:25.267
I'M SO SORRY. OKAY.

14:25.267 --> 14:28.733
TALK TO YOU LATER. BYE.

14:28.733 --> 14:30.400
[ CELL PHONE BEEPS ]

14:32.567 --> 14:33.867
BEFORE YOU SAY ANYTHING,

14:33.867 --> 14:35.933
I KNOW YOU THINK I'M JUST
PLAYING A GAME WITH MALCOLM.

14:35.933 --> 14:37.667
BUT FOR ONCE, I'M NOT.

14:37.667 --> 14:38.867
REALLY.

14:38.867 --> 14:42.267
MM. SO WHAT WAS
THAT ALL ABOUT?

14:42.267 --> 14:43.567
[ SCOFFS ]

14:43.567 --> 14:45.400
WE'VE HUNG OUT THREE TIMES

14:45.400 --> 14:47.933
SINCE HE SAID HE JUST WANTED US
TO BE "FRIENDS."

14:47.933 --> 14:50.100
BUT IT'S BEEN
SO WEIRD AND FAKE,

14:50.100 --> 14:52.333
BECAUSE WE DON'T HAVE
FRIEND ENERGY.

14:52.333 --> 14:56.367
WE HAVE DIRTY, SEXY,
"I WANNA BE YOUR LOVER" ENERGY.

14:56.367 --> 14:57.933
[ CHUCKLES ] OKAY.

14:57.933 --> 15:00.200
WELL, IF YOU'RE BOTH
FEELING THAT,

15:00.200 --> 15:01.433
THEN GET BACK TO IT.

15:01.433 --> 15:02.867
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

15:02.867 --> 15:05.067
HE'S ACTUALLY FINE
WHERE WE ARE NOW.

15:05.067 --> 15:06.700
I'M THE ONE
THAT CAN'T TAKE IT.

15:06.700 --> 15:08.967
LIKE THE OTHER DAY,
WE WERE WALKING --
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

15:08.967 --> 15:12.433
BACK UP.
WHAT DID YOU JUST ADMIT?

15:12.433 --> 15:15.867
YOU CAN'T TAKE WHAT?

15:15.867 --> 15:17.400
DAMN IT.

15:17.400 --> 15:19.467
I KNEW YOU WERE GONNA
HEAR THAT.

15:19.467 --> 15:21.333
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ] OKAY.

15:21.333 --> 15:23.200
YES, I SAID IT.

15:25.067 --> 15:26.267
I LIKE HIM TOO MUCH,

15:26.267 --> 15:27.967
AND I THINK ABOUT HIM
ALL THE TIME.

15:27.967 --> 15:30.767
I HAVEN'T FELT THIS WAY
ABOUT A MAN SINCE SEAN.

15:30.767 --> 15:33.867
YOU'RE FALLING IN LOVE.

15:33.867 --> 15:37.100
[ LAUGHS ]
I AM SO HAPPY FOR YOU.

15:37.100 --> 15:38.433
THIS IS NOT A HAPPY THING.

15:38.433 --> 15:41.167
AND THOSE ARE YOUR WORDS,
NOT MINE.
OH!

15:41.167 --> 15:42.800
HEY, YOU TWO.

15:42.800 --> 15:44.167
HEY, GIRL.

15:44.167 --> 15:46.067
KEISH, I NEED A HUGE FAVOR.

15:46.067 --> 15:47.167
