15:47.167 --> 15:48.700
IT WILL BE, IF YOU CAN
DO THIS FOR ME.

15:48.700 --> 15:50.067
I NEED A SERIOUS HOOKUP.

15:50.067 --> 15:52.600
I GOTTA GET REED INTO THE STUDIO
WITH SUPERTRACKS,

15:52.600 --> 15:53.767
BUT HE'S BOOKED SOLID.

15:53.767 --> 15:54.967
OKAY, BUT AREN'T YOU THE ONE

15:54.967 --> 15:56.533
THAT WORKS AT
A THE RECORD LABEL?

15:56.533 --> 15:58.067
YOU'D HAVE MORE CLOUT
THAN ME.

15:58.067 --> 15:59.900
