A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

16:03.367 --> 16:04.833
AND I KNOW THAT HE WOULD
MOVE MOUNTAINS FOR YOU.

16:04.833 --> 16:07.067
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]
ISN'T THAT THE PRODUCER

16:07.067 --> 16:09.067
THAT'S HAD A CRUSH ON KEISHA
FOR, LIKE, FIVE YEARS?

16:09.067 --> 16:11.700
KEISHA, PLEASE CAN YOU WORK
YOUR MAGIC?

16:13.300 --> 16:15.900
I USE MY FEMININE WILES
FOR ME.

16:15.900 --> 16:17.733
WHY CAN'T YOU USE YOURS
FOR YOU?

16:17.733 --> 16:19.067
PLEASE.

16:21.067 --> 16:22.333
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

16:22.333 --> 16:25.067
APRIL, YOU'RE REALLY TAKING
THIS A&R THING WITH REED

16:25.067 --> 16:26.767
VERY SERIOUSLY.
I'M PROUD OF YOU.

16:26.767 --> 16:29.867
YEAH, WELL, I HAVE NO CHOICE.
I'M PUTTING UP MY OWN MONEY.

16:29.867 --> 16:31.367
WHAT?
WHY?

16:31.367 --> 16:34.700
THEY'VE SHELLED OUT ALL THEY'RE
GONNA SHELL OUT AT THE LABEL.

16:34.700 --> 16:36.067
IT'S A DECISION
THAT I'VE MADE.

16:36.067 --> 16:39.267
