I NEED SUPPORT RIGHT NOW,

16:39.267 --> 16:40.833
NOT CRITICISM.

16:43.800 --> 16:45.667
YOU OWE ME.

16:45.667 --> 16:46.833
[ GASPS AND LAUGHS ]

16:46.833 --> 16:48.600
THANK YOU!
MM-HMM.

