SO YOU CAN STOP FLIPPING OUT.

17:24.600 --> 17:25.767
YOU'RE ENDING IT?

17:25.767 --> 17:27.600
[ CHUCKLES ]
DID IT EVER REALLY BEGIN?

17:27.600 --> 17:29.933
COME OVER TONIGHT SO WE CAN TALK
ABOUT THIS, PLEASE?

17:29.933 --> 17:32.900
