IT WAS JUST SEX.

17:34.600 --> 17:35.767
YOU CAN'T JUST GO AROUND

17:35.767 --> 17:37.767
TOYING WITH PEOPLE'S EMOTIONS,
CHRISTINA.

17:37.767 --> 17:38.933
[ MOUTHS WORD ]

17:38.933 --> 17:40.100
YOU KNOW, SERIOUSLY,

17:40.100 --> 17:42.600
YOU'RE OVER 30,
AND I'M ONLY 21.

17:42.600 --> 17:44.967
I DON'T MEAN TO BE MEAN,

17:44.967 --> 17:48.133
BUT WHY DON'T YOU JUST DO
YOURSELF A FAVOR AND GROW UP?

17:48.133 --> 17:50.500
[ STARTS ENGINE ]

17:52.200 --> 17:58.067
***

17:58.067 --> 18:00.667
KEISHA, YOU ROCK
FOR DOING THIS.

18:00.667 --> 18:02.767
I KNOW.
SERIOUSLY,
WE REALLY APPRECIATE IT.

18:02.767 --> 18:04.333
YEAH, THANKS AGAIN.
I MEAN, SUPERTRACKS IS

18:04.333 --> 18:06.833
ONE OF THE DOPEST PRODUCERS
OUT THERE.

18:06.833 --> 18:08.067
AIN'T THAT KEISHA GREENE?
MM-HMM.

18:08.067 --> 18:11.667
[ LAUGHS ] SORRY, BOO.
YOU ABOUT FIVE YEARS TOO LATE.

18:11.667 --> 18:15.133
MM-HMM.
I'M THE CHICK
THEY CALLING NOW.

18:15.133 --> 18:17.767
***

18:17.767 --> 18:21.167
