THEY'RE SHOOTING A VIDEO.

18:21.167 --> 18:22.333
I MIGHT HAVE TO STOP BY
AND CHECK THAT OUT

18:22.333 --> 18:26.067
WHEN WE'RE DONE.
REED. FOCUS.

18:26.067 --> 18:28.067
***

18:28.067 --> 18:29.933
THE THINGS WE ENDURE
FOR OUR FRIENDS...

18:29.933 --> 18:32.433
[ LAUGHS ]

18:32.433 --> 18:34.067
***

18:34.067 --> 18:36.067
HEY, HEY!

18:36.067 --> 18:38.833
OHH!

18:38.833 --> 18:40.533
MY KEISHA.

18:40.533 --> 18:42.333
MY FUTURE BABY MOTHER.

18:42.333 --> 18:44.333
