FAVORITE GIRL ON THE WALL.

18:47.633 --> 18:50.633
AND, YO, I GOT A TRACK
I JUST GAVE KANYE,

18:50.633 --> 18:53.067
AND I COULD SEE YOU
IN THE VIDEO.

18:53.067 --> 18:55.667
