I STOPPED DOING VIDEOS,

18:55.667 --> 18:57.567
BUT I APPRECIATE THE LOVE.

18:57.567 --> 19:00.433
AND THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR MAKING
TIME FOR MY GIRL APRIL.

19:00.433 --> 19:04.067
ANY FRIEND OF KEISHA
IS A FRIEND OF MINE.

19:04.067 --> 19:05.400
