IN PERSON.

19:07.667 --> 19:09.600
AND THIS IS REED.

19:09.600 --> 19:11.067
REED.

19:11.067 --> 19:13.167
HEY, YOU USED TO BE
WITH THAT GROUP NRG, RIGHT?

19:13.167 --> 19:16.867
