19:49.067 --> 19:51.733
* NO, I CAN'T STOP THINKIN'
I'M WRONG *

19:51.733 --> 19:53.233
* JUST WANTIN' TO KISS YA *

19:53.233 --> 19:56.500
* JUST WANTIN' TO KISS YA
SO LONG, LONG, LONG *

19:56.500 --> 20:00.833
* NOW YOU GONE, GONE, GONE *

20:00.833 --> 20:02.700
OOH!
[ TURNS OFF TRACK ]

20:02.700 --> 20:05.033
MY MAN RIGHT HERE IS FIRE.

20:05.033 --> 20:08.267
YO, I'M-A CLEAR SOME ROOM
OFF MY SCHEDULE,

20:08.267 --> 20:11.267
AND WE GON' DO THIS,
MAKE SOME REAL MONEY.

20:11.267 --> 20:12.467
AND WHILE YOU MAKING
THAT MONEY,

20:12.467 --> 20:14.467
DON'T FORGET TO GET KEISHA
HER FINDER'S FEE.

20:14.467 --> 20:18.533
WE CAN TALK ABOUT THAT
AND OUR FUTURE, BABY.

20:18.533 --> 20:20.000
[ LAUGHS ]

20:20.000 --> 20:22.133
YOU ARE SO FUNNY,
SUPERTRACKS,

20:22.133 --> 20:23.700
BUT I HAVE AN APPOINTMENT.

20:23.700 --> 20:25.233
I'LL CALL YOU, THOUGH.

20:25.233 --> 20:26.600
OH. HOLD UP.

20:26.600 --> 20:30.500
