AND I CAN'T EVEN GET A HUG?

20:30.500 --> 20:32.467
UH-HUH.

20:32.467 --> 20:33.833
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:37.333 --> 20:39.500
[ Strained voice ]
OKAY. OKAY.

20:39.500 --> 20:41.700
MM. MM. OKAY.

20:44.267 --> 20:47.000
ARE YOU SURE
YOU DON'T WANT

20:47.000 --> 20:49.300
TO ROLL UP TO THIS MANSION PARTY
WITH US?

20:49.300 --> 20:51.800
