HE'D GET US IN.

20:51.800 --> 20:53.567
I DON'T KNOW HIM.

20:53.567 --> 20:56.800
BESIDES, I'M TIRED.
I'M GOING HOME.

20:56.800 --> 20:59.867
AND IF YOU WANT A RIDE,
YOU BETTER COME ON.

20:59.867 --> 21:03.300
I'M GOOD. I'LL GET A RIDE.

21:09.900 --> 21:12.133
MMM.

21:12.133 --> 21:15.500
AIN'T NEVER
GONNA BE ANOTHER ONE.

21:16.867 --> 21:19.200
[ CAR ALARM BLARING
IN DISTANCE ]

21:19.200 --> 21:22.467
HEY, YO, TINA.
YOU FEELIN' THAT "E" YET, MA?

21:22.467 --> 21:25.900
'CAUSE IF NOT, I GOT SOME OTHER
GOODIES THAT'LL DO THE TRICK.

21:25.900 --> 21:28.233
Tonya: [ Slurring ] YEAH.
I TOOK BOTH.

21:28.233 --> 21:29.733
AND IT'S TONYA.

21:29.733 --> 21:31.267
IT DON'T MATTER.
COME ON, LET'S JUST GO.

21:31.267 --> 21:33.600
EXCUSE ME, MISS.

21:33.600 --> 21:34.867
DO YOU NEED ANY HELP?

21:34.867 --> 21:37.133
NO, I'M FINE.

21:37.133 --> 21:38.367
I'M REALLY FINE.

21:38.367 --> 21:40.900
LET ME REPHRASE THE QUESTION.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.633
DO YOU KNOW HIM?
NO.

21:42.633 --> 21:44.733
BUT I DON'T KNOW YOU EITHER.

21:44.733 --> 21:47.133
CAN YOU EXCUSE US
FOR A SECOND?

21:47.133 --> 21:48.567
[ STUMBLES ]

21:48.567 --> 21:50.067
I'M-A WAIT IN THE CAR
FOR TWO MINUTES...

21:50.067 --> 21:52.233
MM.
AND I'M OUT. A'IGHT?

21:52.233 --> 21:54.267
***

21:54.267 --> 21:56.700
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT YOU WANT? HMM?

21:56.700 --> 21:58.433
THE QUESTION IS,
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

21:58.433 --> 22:00.100
AND I DON'T THINK IT'S THAT.

22:00.100 --> 22:02.667
HOW'S MY LIFE
ANY OF YOUR BUSINESS?

22:02.667 --> 22:05.200
FOR YOUR INFORMATION, I'M TRYING
TO GET MY NAME OUT THERE,

22:05.200 --> 22:06.467
AND YOU'RE GETTING IN THE WAY
OF THAT.

22:06.467 --> 22:09.067
OH, I'M SORRY FOR STOPPING YOU
FROM GETTING IN A CAR

22:09.067 --> 22:13.067
WITH A GUY YOU JUST MET,
ALL DRUGGED UP ON ECSTASY.

22:13.067 --> 22:14.633
GO AHEAD THEN.
GET YOUR NAME OUT THERE.

22:14.633 --> 22:17.867
PLEASE. LIKE YOU DIDN'T
USED TO DO THE SAME THING?

22:17.867 --> 22:19.467
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T GET
IN ALL THOSE VIDEOS

22:19.467 --> 22:21.967
BASED ON YOUR LOOKS
OR YOUR DANCING.

22:21.967 --> 22:23.933
YOU WEREN'T ALL THAT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:23.933 --> 22:25.900
BELIEVE ME, LITTLE GIRL.

22:25.900 --> 22:28.167
I NEVER PLAYED MYSELF
LIKE YOU'RE ABOUT TO.

22:28.167 --> 22:30.067
MM-HMM. MM-HMM.

22:30.067 --> 22:31.267
MM.

22:31.267 --> 22:32.967
OHH.

22:32.967 --> 22:35.433
I NEED TO SIT DOWN.
IT'S KICKING IN.

22:35.433 --> 22:37.167
MM.

22:37.167 --> 22:40.333
[ GIGGLES ]

22:40.333 --> 22:43.200
CAN YOU GIVE ME A RIDE
TO THE PARTY?

