***

22:55.267 --> 22:58.133
MM. WELL...

22:58.133 --> 22:59.833
GOOD MORNING.

22:59.833 --> 23:03.067
YOU CAN'T BE THAT SAME
IMPOLITE GIRL I MET LAST NIGHT.

23:03.067 --> 23:06.233
THANK YOU
FOR TAKING CARE OF ME.

23:06.233 --> 23:08.067
I REALLY NEEDED THAT.

23:08.067 --> 23:10.900
I CAN'T BELIEVE I MISSED
THAT PARTY, THOUGH.

23:10.900 --> 23:12.667
I WAS TRYING TO MEET AKON.

23:12.667 --> 23:15.400
I HOPE THAT'S NOT
HOW YOU USUALLY OPERATE.

23:15.400 --> 23:17.167
WHAT'S THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

23:17.167 --> 23:19.100
CALM DOWN. I'M NOT JUDGING.

23:19.100 --> 23:21.400
I'VE JUST BEEN IN THE GAME
A LITTLE LONGER THAN YOU,

23:21.400 --> 23:25.067
AND I'VE SEEN GIRLS LIKE YOU,
ALL STARSTRUCK

23:25.067 --> 23:27.933
AND IMPRESSED BY THE MANSIONS,
THE CARS, AND THE JEWELS.

23:27.933 --> 23:30.833
PLEASE. I'M NOT IMPRESSED
BY ANY OF THAT.

23:30.833 --> 23:34.067
MY DADDY COULD BUY AND SELL
MOST OF THESE DUDES.

23:34.067 --> 23:36.200
OKAY, SO YOU'RE
A LITTLE RICH GIRL.

23:36.200 --> 23:38.067
DADDY'S LITTLE PRINCESS.

23:38.067 --> 23:39.433
HELL, NO.

23:39.433 --> 23:41.167
HE WANTS ME TO HAVE
A CORNBALL LIFE

23:41.167 --> 23:42.533
WHERE I GET MARRIED
TO SOME DOCTOR.

23:42.533 --> 23:45.833
THAT IS NOT ME.
I'M TRYING TO BLOW UP.

23:45.833 --> 23:47.167
OF COURSE.

23:47.167 --> 23:49.567
AND IF PARTYING WITH THESE DUDES
HELPS ME TO DO THAT,

23:49.567 --> 23:51.267
THEN SO BE IT.

23:51.267 --> 23:53.900
OKAY. THAT'S DEFINITELY
A PLAN.

23:53.900 --> 23:55.800
BUT AFTER YOU PISS OFF
YOUR DADDY

23:55.800 --> 23:58.667
AND PLAY EVERY GUY IN TOWN,
THEN WHAT?

23:58.667 --> 24:00.700
THEN I GOT WHAT I WANT.
THEN I'M FAMOUS.

24:00.700 --> 24:03.433
SO YOU'RE FAMOUS?
THEN WHAT?

24:03.433 --> 24:05.733
THEN I GET MY REALITY SHOW.

24:05.733 --> 24:08.300
OKAY, SO NOW YOU'RE OVEREXPOSED
AND INFAMOUS.

24:08.300 --> 24:09.967
THEN WHAT?
THEN I'M WALKING
THE RED CARPET

24:09.967 --> 24:12.133
AT THE GRAMMYS
AND AT MOVIE PREMIERES.

24:12.133 --> 24:13.300
OKAY, THEN WHAT?

24:13.300 --> 24:15.433
THEN I DON'T KNOW.

24:15.433 --> 24:18.533
DAMN. WHY ARE YOU ASKING ME
ALL THESE QUESTIONS?

24:26.067 --> 24:28.300
BECAUSE YOU SHOULD KNOW

24:28.300 --> 24:32.067
THAT THE COST OF THOSE
FEW MOMENTS IN THE LIMELIGHT

24:32.067 --> 24:34.433
WILL ROB YOU
OF YOUR INTEGRITY.

24:34.433 --> 24:38.233
AND IT MAY NOT MEAN ANYTHING
TO YOU NOW,

24:38.233 --> 24:39.400
BUT IT WILL.

24:39.400 --> 24:41.733
BUT --
LOOK.

24:41.733 --> 24:43.767
JUST GO HOME
AND THINK ABOUT IT.

24:43.767 --> 24:47.533
AND SPEAKING OF HOME,
LET'S GET YOU THERE.

24:49.833 --> 24:52.933
[ LORI MICHAELS' "GET IT THROUGH
YOUR HEAD" PLAYING ]

24:54.933 --> 24:56.967
* OOH *

24:59.067 --> 25:01.067
* I THOUGHT I HAD A BAD FEELING
WHEN WE MET *

25:01.067 --> 25:02.400
THIS IS WHERE YOU LIVE?

25:02.400 --> 25:04.633
THIS IS WHERE
MY BROTHER LIVES.

25:04.633 --> 25:07.233
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

25:07.233 --> 25:09.833
[ GATE OPENS]

25:09.833 --> 25:12.567
* GET A GRIP NOW *

25:12.567 --> 25:15.867
* YOU KEEP CREEPING TO ME WHEN
YOU KNOW IT AIN'T ALL RIGHT *

25:15.867 --> 25:18.800
* IT'S LOOKING LIKE
I GOT SOMETHING TO HIDE *

25:18.800 --> 25:22.233
* I'D HAVE SOME EXPLAINING
TO DO *

25:24.433 --> 25:26.367
TONYA, WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN?

25:26.367 --> 25:28.133
I'VE BEEN CALLING YOU
ALL NIGHT.

25:28.133 --> 25:29.867
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

25:29.867 --> 25:33.367
OBVIOUSLY, I CAN
TAKE CARE OF MYSELF.

25:33.367 --> 25:35.400
HER VERSION OF
TAKING CARE OF HERSELF

25:35.400 --> 25:37.467
IS DROPPING
TWO ECSTASY PILLS

25:37.467 --> 25:40.833
AND GETTING INTO
A STRANGE MAN'S CAR.

25:40.833 --> 25:42.900
HE DIDN'T NEED TO KNOW
ALL THAT.

25:42.900 --> 25:44.500
WHY YOU GOTTA COME OVER HERE,
STARTIN' DRAMA?

25:44.500 --> 25:46.300
HOW DO YOU TWO
EVEN KNOW EACH OTHER?

25:46.300 --> 25:48.233
HOW DO YOU TWO KNOW
EACH OTHER?

25:49.700 --> 25:52.100
OH. IS THIS
ONE OF YOUR FRIENDS?

25:52.100 --> 25:54.067
TONYA, DON'T LET YOUR MOUTH
GET YOU INTO MORE TROUBLE,

25:54.067 --> 25:55.233
ALL RIGHT?

25:55.233 --> 25:58.867
LOOK, SHE'S OKAY.
SHE'S HERE, SO I'M GONNA GO.

25:58.867 --> 26:01.467
ACTUALLY, I'D LIKE YOU TO STAY,
SHE'S GONNA GO,

26:01.467 --> 26:03.500
WHERE AM I GOING?
STAY WHERE?

26:03.500 --> 26:05.433
STAY HERE WHILE
I DROP HER OFF AT OUR DAD'S.

26:05.433 --> 26:08.067
I REALLY WANNA TALK TO YOU
ABOUT SOMETHING.

26:08.067 --> 26:09.333
I HAVE THINGS TO DO.

26:09.333 --> 26:11.567
IT'S SOMETHING IMPORTANT,
KEISHA. OKAY?

26:11.567 --> 26:13.167
I'LL BE BACK IN 30 MINUTES.

26:15.067 --> 26:17.467
PLEASE.

26:18.933 --> 26:20.133
OKAY.

26:23.433 --> 26:26.267
LET'S GO.

26:26.267 --> 26:27.667
Val: [ LAUGHS ] DON'T RUN!

26:27.667 --> 26:29.800
[ GRUNTING ] OOH!

26:29.800 --> 26:31.433
NO FAIR. YOU CHEATED.

26:31.433 --> 26:33.300
HOW? I KNOCKED YOU OUT.

26:33.300 --> 26:36.500
NO. I WAS DISTRACTED
BY YOUR DUMB IDEA.

26:36.500 --> 26:40.067
COME ON, VAL.
LOOK, JUST HEAR ME OUT.

26:40.067 --> 26:44.067
IT TURNS OUT
BEING GAY IS FABULOUS.

26:44.067 --> 26:45.233
MY TWITTER IS ALL ATWITTER.

26:45.233 --> 26:47.667
I HAVE SIX
NEW FACEBOOK FAN PAGES.

26:47.667 --> 26:50.100
AND FOR EVERY SPONSOR
THAT'S FALLEN OUT,

26:50.100 --> 26:51.667
I'VE GOTTEN TWO MORE.

26:51.667 --> 26:54.433
I MEAN, WHO KNEW IT TURNS OUT
BEING GAY IS THE NEW BLACK?

26:54.433 --> 26:57.500
OKAY. WELL, THAT'S GREAT
FOR YOU. BUT WHAT ABOUT ME?

26:57.500 --> 26:59.200
HERE'S HOW YOU COME IN.

26:59.200 --> 27:02.400
WE KEEP THIS COUPLE THING GOING
FOR A FEW MORE MONTHS.

27:02.400 --> 27:06.067
THEN AFTER MY PREMIERE,
AFTER I'VE GOTTEN GOOD NUMBERS,

27:06.067 --> 27:08.100
YOU CAN BREAK UP WITH ME.

27:08.100 --> 27:09.767
YOU JUST HAVE TO TIME IT
SO IT'S DURING SWEEPS.

27:09.767 --> 27:11.700
SO WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN NOVEMBER?

27:11.700 --> 27:13.833
SHARON, YOU'RE ALWAYS TRYING
TO CONVINCE ME

27:13.833 --> 27:15.200
TO DO SOMETHING CRAZY,

27:15.200 --> 27:16.733
JUST LIKE THAT NIGHT.

27:16.733 --> 27:18.833
AW, HELL, NO!
THAT'S THE STORY YOU TELLIN'?

27:18.833 --> 27:21.600
IF YOU WOULD'VE JUST PAID
YOUR HALF OF THE HEATING BILL,

27:21.600 --> 27:23.700
WE WOULD'VE HAVE
HAD TO CUDDLE TO KEEP WARM.

27:23.700 --> 27:26.567
THAT'S ALL I WAS DOING,
WAS CUDDLING.

27:26.567 --> 27:27.900
YOU WERE DOING OTHER THINGS.

27:27.900 --> 27:30.200
YEAH. I WAS SLEEPING.

27:30.200 --> 27:32.967
OH! WHO SLEEPS NAKED
WHEN THEY'RE COLD?

27:32.967 --> 27:35.367
ALL THE MAGAZINES SAY THAT IS
THE BEST WAY TO KEEP WARM.

27:35.367 --> 27:38.500
BESIDES, YOU ARE THE ONE
WHO SUGGESTED WE DO SHOTS.

27:38.500 --> 27:40.133
LOOK, I WAS A SOUTHERN BELLE

27:40.133 --> 27:42.367
STEEPED IN TRADITIONAL
SOUTHERN VALUES.

27:42.367 --> 27:47.700
YOU WERE A NEW YORK CITY GIRL
LIVING LIFE IN THE FAST LANE,

27:47.700 --> 27:49.500
TRYING DIFFERENT THINGS.

27:49.500 --> 27:50.800
I NEVER STOOD A CHANCE.

27:50.800 --> 27:53.867
SHARON, LOOK AT ME
AND LOOK AT YOU.

27:53.867 --> 27:56.967
BETWEEN THE TWO OF US,
WHO NEVER STOOD A CHANCE?

27:56.967 --> 28:00.233
I THINK OBVIOUSLY THE TRUTH
NEVER STOOD A CHANCE.

28:00.233 --> 28:02.967
YOU WERE DELUSIONAL THEN
AND YOU'RE DELUSIONAL NOW.

28:02.967 --> 28:05.100
I AM NOT GOING TO BE A PART
OF YOUR HOAX.

28:05.100 --> 28:07.967
JUST DO THIS FOR ME, VAL.
I NEED THIS.

28:07.967 --> 28:09.067
OH. [ CHUCKLES ]

28:09.067 --> 28:11.533
THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID
THAT NIGHT, TOO.

28:11.533 --> 28:15.667
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW WHAT I SAID
IF YOU WAS SO ASLEEP?

28:15.667 --> 28:17.900
GOOD-BYE, SHARON.

28:17.900 --> 28:20.667
Man: * I KEEP GETTING
THESE RAINDROPS *

28:20.667 --> 28:22.800
* FALLING ON MY HEAD *

28:22.800 --> 28:24.900
YOU KNOW, I DIDN'T SIGN UP
FOR THIS, MAN.

28:24.900 --> 28:26.367
I WAS FEELIN' REED.

28:26.367 --> 28:28.433
AND IF I WANTED ANOTHER ONE
OF YOUR ARTISTS,

28:28.433 --> 28:29.867
I'D BE DOING THAT.

28:29.867 --> 28:33.067
HEY, GUYS, WHAT'S GOING ON?
WHERE'S REED?

28:33.067 --> 28:35.233
APRIL, THAT IS THE QUESTION.
WHERE IS REED?

28:35.233 --> 28:38.467
HE ISN'T HERE? HE TEXTED ME
AN HOUR AGO AND SAID HE WAS.

28:38.467 --> 28:40.900
HE LIED.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

28:40.900 --> 28:42.300
BOTH OF Y'ALL ARE WASTING
MY TIME. I'M OUT.

28:42.300 --> 28:43.633
[ CELL PHONE VIBRATES ]
I'M GETTING A CALL NOW.

28:43.633 --> 28:44.800
WAIT.

28:44.800 --> 28:46.500
REED? WHERE THE HELL ARE YOU?

28:46.500 --> 28:47.933
Woman: Ma'am, this isn't Reed.

28:47.933 --> 28:49.733
THEN WHO IS IT? YOU KNOW,
PUT REED ON THE PHONE.

28:49.733 --> 28:51.300
THIS IS AN EMERGENCY.

28:51.300 --> 28:53.167
I'M CALLING FROM
ATLANTA GENERAL HOSPITAL,

28:53.167 --> 28:55.300
AND YOUR NUMBER WAS
THE LAST ONE DIALED.

28:55.300 --> 28:58.200
Are you a relative?

28:58.200 --> 29:00.967
YES. WHAT'S GOING ON?

29:00.967 --> 29:04.333
I'M SORRY TO TELL YOU THIS,
BUT...

29:04.333 --> 29:06.433
MR. DURHAM OVERDOSED.

29:06.433 --> 29:09.400
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

29:09.400 --> 29:11.267
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

29:13.767 --> 29:16.500
THANKS FOR WAITING.

29:16.500 --> 29:18.767
SO WHAT'S SO IMPORTANT
I HAD TO STAY?

29:18.767 --> 29:20.400
FIRST OFF,
I REALLY WANNA THANK YOU

29:20.400 --> 29:23.067
FOR WHAT YOU DID
FOR MY SISTER --

29:23.067 --> 29:25.267
FOR STOPPING HER
FROM GOING WITH THAT GUY

29:25.267 --> 29:26.700
AND FOR WHATEVER YOU SAID
TO HER.

29:26.700 --> 29:28.333
YOU'RE THE ONLY PERSON
IN A LONG TIME

29:28.333 --> 29:30.367
THAT ACTUALLY
KNOCKED SOME SENSE

29:30.367 --> 29:32.467
INTO THAT HARD LITTLE HEAD
OF HERS.

29:32.467 --> 29:34.367
HOW'D I DO THAT?
WELL, FOR THE FIRST TIME,

29:34.367 --> 29:37.167
SHE'S QUESTIONING WHAT TO DO
WITH HER LIFE.

29:37.167 --> 29:39.867
WOW.

29:39.867 --> 29:41.200
I'M GLAD I COULD HELP.

29:41.200 --> 29:44.133
YEAH. I'VE BEEN...

29:44.133 --> 29:47.167
I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT
A LOT OF THINGS.

29:47.167 --> 29:50.567
AND LET ME START WITH
WHY I BOUGHT JASMINE'S BOOK.

29:50.567 --> 29:52.433
OKAY.

29:52.433 --> 29:53.733
IT WAS BECAUSE OF TONYA.

29:55.167 --> 29:57.867
TONYA GOT...

29:57.867 --> 30:01.600
CAUGHT UP A FEW YEARS AGO
AND ACTUALLY DID SOME PORN.

30:01.600 --> 30:02.767
JASMINE WROTE ABOUT IT,

30:02.767 --> 30:04.500
SO I BOUGHT THE BOOK TO
COVER IT UP

30:04.500 --> 30:05.867
'CAUSE IT WOULD'VE KILLED
MY FATHER,

30:05.867 --> 30:08.100
OR HE WOULD'VE KILLED
SOMEBODY ELSE.

30:08.100 --> 30:09.467
WHOA.

30:09.467 --> 30:10.833
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

30:12.700 --> 30:15.833
THANK YOU FOR TRUSTING ME
WITH THAT.

30:15.833 --> 30:19.100
I HATE WHAT MY SISTER DID,

30:19.100 --> 30:20.433
BUT IT WAS HER MISTAKE,

30:20.433 --> 30:23.033
AND I DAMN SURE WASN'T GONNA
LET JASMINE MAKE IT WORSE.

30:25.167 --> 30:26.533
WELL...

30:29.667 --> 30:31.300
SINCE WERE BEING HONEST,

30:31.300 --> 30:33.533
THERE'S SOMETHING I'VE BEEN
WANTING TO TELL YOU

30:33.533 --> 30:35.867
FOR QUITE SOME TIME MYSELF.

30:35.867 --> 30:37.267
I'M LISTENING.

30:38.967 --> 30:43.900
REMEMBER WHEN I TOLD YOU I DID
SOME THINGS I WASN'T PROUD OF?

30:43.900 --> 30:45.500
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

30:45.500 --> 30:48.000
WELL, ONE OF THOSE THINGS

30:48.000 --> 30:50.200
WAS STEALING YOUR WATCH
ON CAM'RON'S SET.

30:50.200 --> 30:54.100
AND I'M SORRY I LIED
ABOUT THAT.

30:54.100 --> 30:56.633
OKAY.

30:58.033 --> 31:00.567
I REALLY DIDN'T KNOW
IT WAS YOURS.

31:00.567 --> 31:03.667
BUT JASMINE SAID IF I DIDN'T
TAKE IT, SHE'D WRITE ABOUT

31:03.667 --> 31:05.867
THE STUPID STUFF I DID
YEARS AGO.

31:07.600 --> 31:10.067
I COULDN'T LET THAT HAPPEN.

31:11.900 --> 31:13.767
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING
RIGHT NOW?

31:13.767 --> 31:14.933
I'M THINKING
THAT I APPRECIATE

31:14.933 --> 31:17.833
HOW REAL WE'RE BEING
WITH EACH OTHER,

31:17.833 --> 31:19.800
AND HOW REFRESHING THAT IS.

31:22.133 --> 31:24.600
THAT'S NOT THE RESPONSE
I WAS EXPECTING.

31:24.600 --> 31:28.833
I RESPECT YOU FOR TELLING ME,
OKAY?

31:28.833 --> 31:32.333
AND ORDINARILY, YEAH,
IT WOULD BE A DEALBREAKER.

31:32.333 --> 31:35.967
LISTEN, BOTTOM LINE IS,
I MESSED UP.

31:35.967 --> 31:37.333
OKAY?

31:39.300 --> 31:40.967
AND I MISS YOU.

31:42.500 --> 31:44.600
AND I WANNA BE WITH YOU.

31:44.600 --> 31:47.100
WAIT.

31:47.100 --> 31:50.367
ARE YOU SAYING...
I'M SAYING LET'S DO THIS,

31:50.367 --> 31:53.067
OR AT LEAST LET'S TRY.

31:54.367 --> 31:57.067
MALCOLM, PLEASE DON'T PLAY
WITH MY HEART,

31:57.067 --> 31:59.067
BECAUSE IT'S REALLY IN THIS.

31:59.067 --> 32:01.700
MINE IS, TOO.

32:04.067 --> 32:06.867
WHAT'S WRONG, BABY?

32:08.533 --> 32:11.433
I JUST NEVER THOUGHT
WE'D GET HERE.

32:37.067 --> 32:38.867
[ KEYS CLATTER ]

32:38.867 --> 32:40.400
BATHROOM'S THERE.

32:40.400 --> 32:42.267
I'LL GRAB YOU SOME BLANKETS.

32:43.600 --> 32:46.333
YO, COULD I GET
A LITTLE SYMPATHY?

32:46.333 --> 32:48.667
SYMPATHY?

32:48.667 --> 32:51.200
WHAT'S THE ONE THING
I TOLD YOU NOT TO DO?

32:51.200 --> 32:53.633
WASTE MY MONEY,
AND THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT YOU DID.

32:53.633 --> 32:56.100
SO SLEEP IT OFF, I'LL GIVE YOU
A RIDE HOME IN THE MORNING,

32:56.100 --> 32:58.867
AND WE'RE DONE.

32:58.867 --> 33:01.400
YO, YOU DO REALIZE YOU JUST
PICKED ME UP FROM THE HOSPITAL.

33:01.400 --> 33:02.567
FOR PARTYING!

33:02.567 --> 33:04.167
OH, OH, POOR YOU!

33:04.167 --> 33:06.067
I DID TOO MAY LINES,
I POPPED TOO MANY PILLS --

33:06.067 --> 33:07.233
ALL AT THE SAME TIME.

33:07.233 --> 33:10.233
AND BY THE WAY,
YOU'RE DOING IT BACKWARDS.

33:10.233 --> 33:12.067
CAN YOU BURN OUT
AFTER YOU'VE MADE IT?

33:12.067 --> 33:13.333
MAN, WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM ME?

33:13.333 --> 33:17.467
A LITTLE DAMN PROFESSIONALISM
AND RESPECT!

33:17.467 --> 33:19.833
FOR YOURSELF AND ME.

33:19.833 --> 33:22.667
WHY AM I HAVING THIS
CONVERSATION? GOOD NIGHT, REED.

33:22.667 --> 33:23.967
APRIL, PLEASE,
CAN I JUST SAY SOMETHIN'?

33:25.733 --> 33:28.767
I'M SORRY FOR REAL.

33:28.767 --> 33:30.067
HOW MANY SORRYS?

33:30.067 --> 33:31.567
SAY SOMETHING DIFFERENT
FOR A CHANGE.

33:31.567 --> 33:34.333
YEAH, OKAY, FINE.
YOU WANNA KNOW THE TRUTH?

33:34.333 --> 33:36.167
YOU WANNA KNOW WHY IT'S SO HARD
TO GO IN THE STUDIO?

33:36.167 --> 33:37.600
YOU KNOW WHY I CAN'T FINISH
MY ALBUM?

33:37.600 --> 33:39.367
YOU KNOW WHY I GET HIGH?

33:42.500 --> 33:44.300
I'M AFRAID TO FAIL.

33:49.067 --> 33:51.733
YOU DON'T EVEN UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU HAVE.

33:51.733 --> 33:55.333
YOU HAVE THIS BEAUTIFUL,
SOULFUL VOICE.

33:55.333 --> 33:56.667
AND WHEN YOU SING
WHAT'S IN YOUR HEART,

33:56.667 --> 33:58.667
YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT FAILURE.

33:58.667 --> 34:02.067
EVEN IF PEOPLE DON'T LIKE IT,
YOU'VE BEEN TRUE TO YOURSELF.

34:02.067 --> 34:05.067
JUST BE AN ARTIST, REED.

34:05.067 --> 34:07.733
LET ME WORRY ABOUT THE REST.

34:07.733 --> 34:10.433
WELL, SO WE'RE NOT DONE?

34:10.433 --> 34:11.600
ARE YOU STILL GONNA WORK
WITH ME?

34:11.600 --> 34:13.267
[ SIGHS ]

34:15.067 --> 34:17.300
HERE ARE THE RULES --

34:17.300 --> 34:18.467
NO MORE DRUGS,

34:18.467 --> 34:20.767
NO MORE FLAKING
ON STUDIO TIME,

34:20.767 --> 34:21.967
NO MORE BITCHING
ABOUT THE SKILLS

34:21.967 --> 34:23.167
YOU THINK
YOU DON'T HAVE HAVE.

34:23.167 --> 34:25.733
JUST WRITE AND SING.

34:25.733 --> 34:28.100
OH, AND ONE MORE THING --

34:28.100 --> 34:30.900
YOU'RE SLEEPING ON MY COUCH
UNTIL WE FINISH THIS ALBUM,

34:30.900 --> 34:32.267
SO GET COMFORTABLE.

34:35.067 --> 34:38.267
AND ACCORDING TO
HOSPITAL OFFICIALS,

34:38.267 --> 34:41.433
MOTHER AND ALL SIX BABIES
ARE DOING JUST FINE.

34:42.767 --> 34:45.833
ON ANOTHER NOTE, I WAS HOPING
IT WOULD DIE DOWN ON ITS OWN,

34:45.833 --> 34:49.400
BUT THE MEDIA CIRCUS AROUND
THE QUESTION OF MY SEXUALITY

34:49.400 --> 34:50.833
HAS GOTTEN OUT OF HAND.

34:50.833 --> 34:53.133
NOT SINCE THE COUNTRY WAITED
WITH BAITED BREATH

34:53.133 --> 34:56.133
TO SEE IF THE CHILEAN MINERS
WOULD EMERGE SAFELY

34:56.133 --> 35:00.067
HAS A STORY SO CAPTIVATED
THE AMERICAN PUBLIC.

35:00.067 --> 35:01.233
I CANNOT LEAVE MY HOUSE

35:01.233 --> 35:04.333
WITHOUT A CAMERA OR A MIC
BEING SHOVED IN MY FACE.

35:04.333 --> 35:07.067
JENNIFER ANISTON, I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT, GIRL.

35:07.067 --> 35:09.467
I DIDN'T ASK FOR THIS SITUATION,

35:09.467 --> 35:12.667
AND I CERTAINLY DIDN'T
DO ANYTHING TO EXPLOIT IT.

35:12.667 --> 35:14.233
I'M A VICTIM.

35:14.233 --> 35:16.833
BUT WHO I FEEL MOST SORRY FOR

35:16.833 --> 35:18.733
IS POOR LITTLE VAL STOKES.

35:18.733 --> 35:22.067
JUST ASK HER.
SHE'S DEFENSELESS.

35:22.067 --> 35:23.233
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE,

35:23.233 --> 35:25.200
TO SPEAK UP FOR
THE LITTLE PEOPLE.

35:25.200 --> 35:27.667
AND MAKE PRIVACY A PRIME TOPIC

35:27.667 --> 35:31.500
ON MY NEW SYNDICATED TALK SHOW
THAT JUST GOT AN EARLY PICKUP,

35:31.500 --> 35:34.233
AIRING MONDAY THROUGH FRIDAY
AT 4:00.

35:34.233 --> 35:37.467
YES, OPRAH, I GOT YOUR SLOT.

35:40.300 --> 35:41.500
[ TURNS OFF TV ]

35:42.833 --> 35:44.167
WELL, VAL,

35:44.167 --> 35:47.500
I GUESS YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S
GONNA KEEP US IN SUSPENSE.

35:47.500 --> 35:50.200
SHE'S JUST PLAYING ANOTHER ANGLE
FOR THE PUBLIC,

35:50.200 --> 35:51.900
TRYING TO GET MORE RATINGS.

35:51.900 --> 35:56.467
MM. I GUESS YOU NEVER KNOW
WHAT'S REAL THEN.

35:56.467 --> 35:58.333
WELL...

35:58.333 --> 36:01.367
YOU MAY NOT KNOW
WHAT'S REAL WITH HER,

36:01.367 --> 36:03.600
BUT I HOPE YOU KNOW
WHAT'S REAL WITH ME.

36:03.600 --> 36:05.267
MM.

36:05.267 --> 36:07.333
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

36:07.333 --> 36:08.700
WHAT'S THAT LOOK?

36:08.700 --> 36:11.067
I WANNA KISS YOU.

36:11.067 --> 36:14.533
THEN I THINK...
[Whispers ] YOU SHOULD DO THAT.

36:14.533 --> 36:17.567
***

36:28.200 --> 36:29.767
THAT FEEL REAL?

36:29.767 --> 36:31.467
NO.

36:31.467 --> 36:34.933
THAT FELT UNREAL.

36:34.933 --> 36:37.167
***

36:37.167 --> 36:38.433
Man: * WE'D BE TEARING UP
THE PLACE *

36:38.433 --> 36:42.700
***

36:42.700 --> 36:43.867
* TELL ME *

36:43.867 --> 36:46.633
* 'CAUSE I NEED IT
LIKE I NEED YA *

36:46.633 --> 36:51.300
***

36:51.300 --> 36:53.067
* YEAH, YEAH, YEAH *

36:53.067 --> 36:54.567
* YEAH, YEAH, YEAH *

36:54.567 --> 36:56.267
***

36:56.267 --> 36:57.867
Both: [ CHUCKLE ]

36:57.867 --> 37:00.600
MM. AS MUCH AS I HATE
TO LEAVE,

37:00.600 --> 37:04.667
I'M GONNA SHOWER AND GO
BECAUSE I HAVE TO GET UP EARLY.

37:04.667 --> 37:06.467
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

37:06.467 --> 37:08.733
YOU HAVE TO GET UP EARLY?

37:10.133 --> 37:11.933
TO DO WHAT?

37:11.933 --> 37:16.733
I...I JUST HAVE A LOT OF STUFF
TO DO TOMORROW.

37:16.733 --> 37:17.967
MM-HMM.

37:19.600 --> 37:21.233
I'M SORRY.

37:21.233 --> 37:22.467
[ SIGHS ]

37:22.467 --> 37:24.333
I'M SO USED TO LEAVING
RIGHT AFTER.

37:24.333 --> 37:28.933
OH, THAT SOUNDS TERRIBLE,
DOESN'T IT?

37:28.933 --> 37:30.767
WHAT'S TERRIBLE

37:30.767 --> 37:33.433
IS THAT YOU NEVER HAD ANYBODY
WORTH STAYING FOR.

37:33.433 --> 37:36.067
NOW YOU DO.

37:36.067 --> 37:38.433
SO YOU'RE WELCOME TO SHOWER.

37:38.433 --> 37:40.233
IN FACT, I'LL JOIN YOU.

37:41.867 --> 37:43.900
BUT YOU AIN'T LEAVING.

37:48.600 --> 37:51.467
[ FIRE CRACKLING ]

37:52.933 --> 37:54.300
[ GRUNTS ]

38:17.633 --> 38:19.900
[Whispers ] APRIL?
YOU ASLEEP?

38:26.733 --> 38:29.767
[ KISSES ]

38:29.767 --> 38:31.333
[ INHALES SHARPLY ] GOD!

38:31.333 --> 38:33.133
OW! WHOA!

38:33.133 --> 38:34.500
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

38:34.500 --> 38:35.900
I WAS JUST SHOWING YOU
A LITTLE LOVE

38:35.900 --> 38:37.400
FOR THE LOVE YOU SHOWING ME.

38:37.400 --> 38:38.933
OKAY, REED,

38:38.933 --> 38:41.833
I AM GONNA SAY THIS
ONE MORE TIME.
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

38:41.833 --> 38:44.100
YOU'RE NOT MY TYPE,

38:44.100 --> 38:45.767
AND THIS ISN'T
THAT KIND OF PARTY.

38:45.767 --> 38:46.933
OKAY?

38:46.933 --> 38:49.067
LET'S JUST PRETEND
THIS NEVER HAPPENED

38:49.067 --> 38:50.200
AND HAVE
A GOOD NIGHT'S SLEEP.

38:50.200 --> 38:52.067
SEE, I WAS JUST -- I WAS JUST
FEELING APPRECIATIVE.

38:52.067 --> 38:53.833
PUT IT IN A SONG.

38:55.567 --> 38:57.067
[Whispers ] ALL RIGHT.

39:00.067 --> 39:03.100
[ APRIL HILL'S "THE SEARCH"
PLAYING ]

39:06.333 --> 39:07.500
* COME ON *

39:07.500 --> 39:14.333
***

39:14.333 --> 39:16.267
MORNING, BEAUTIFUL.

39:16.267 --> 39:19.200
GOOD MORNING, HANDSOME.

39:19.200 --> 39:20.767
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
I'M GONNA GET USED TO THIS.

39:20.767 --> 39:23.167
THAT'S WHAT I'M HOPIN'.

39:23.167 --> 39:24.933
[ KNIFE CLANKS ]
MMM.

39:24.933 --> 39:26.100
WHAT?
MMM.

39:26.100 --> 39:27.767
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
TELL ME.

39:27.767 --> 39:29.567
[ KNIFE SCRAPING ]
MNH.

39:29.567 --> 39:31.400
OHH.

39:31.400 --> 39:34.633
YOU CAN'T BELIEVE
I GOT YOU DOING THIS, HUH?

39:34.633 --> 39:36.233
YOU LIKE ME.

39:36.233 --> 39:37.400
I MUST LIKE YOU

39:37.400 --> 39:39.433
IF I'M SITTING HERE,
PUTTING BUTTER ON YOUR TOAST.

39:39.433 --> 39:40.600
YOU KNOW WHAT? YOU DO IT.

39:40.600 --> 39:42.333
NO. I LIKE IT WHEN
YOU DO IT.

39:42.333 --> 39:44.200
THAT'S 'CAUSE
YOU LIKE ME, TOO.

39:44.200 --> 39:46.100
YEAH. I DO.

39:46.100 --> 39:47.700
***

39:47.700 --> 39:49.900
I REALLY DO.

39:49.900 --> 39:54.667
***

39:54.667 --> 39:57.267
DON'T KISS NOBODY ELSE
LIKE THIS, KEISHA.

39:58.633 --> 40:00.067
I'M NOT PLAYIN'.

40:00.067 --> 40:03.233
DON'T BUTTER NOBODY ELSE'S
TOAST, MALCOLM.

40:03.233 --> 40:04.967
I'M NOT PLAYIN'.

40:04.967 --> 40:10.400
***

40:10.400 --> 40:13.800
[ GIGGLING ]

40:13.800 --> 40:15.033
[ Singsongy ] YOU LIKE ME.

40:15.033 --> 40:17.167
Both: [ LAUGH ]

40:17.167 --> 40:18.733
MM-HMM.

40:18.733 --> 40:24.667
***

40:26.767 --> 40:28.467
NEXT ON "SINGLE LADIES"...

40:28.467 --> 40:30.567
[ GASPS ] QUINN?
OH, HELL, NO.

40:30.567 --> 40:32.900
[ SINGS INDISTINCTLY ]

40:32.900 --> 40:35.100
I'M GLAD TO SEE
YOU'RE HARD AT WORK.

40:35.100 --> 40:36.533
Keisha: HI, LADIES!

40:36.533 --> 40:38.100
WELCOME TO MY BRUNCH.

40:38.100 --> 40:41.100
WHAT'S UP, MALCOLM? GUESS MY
INVITATION GOT LOST IN THE MAIL.

40:41.100 --> 40:42.867
THIS IS MY LITTLE BROTHER
TERRENCE.

40:42.867 --> 40:44.200
[ SLAPS HANDS ]

40:44.200 --> 40:46.600
[ Lowered voice ] WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

40:46.600 --> 40:48.033
I WANT YOU BACK.

40:48.033 --> 40:50.100
I AM WITH SOMEONE.
IT'S JERRY.

40:50.100 --> 40:51.267
JERRY WHO?

40:51.267 --> 40:53.767
WATERS.
OF ALL THE DUDES,

40:53.767 --> 40:55.933
YOU PICKED THE OWNER
OF MY TEAM?

40:55.933 --> 40:57.767
THANK YOU FOR STANDING UP
FOR ME, BABE.

40:57.767 --> 40:59.300
IF YOU HAD JUST STAYED OUT OF IT
LIKE I TOLD YOU TO,

40:59.300 --> 41:00.967
THIS NEVER WOULD'VE HAPPENED.

41:00.967 --> 41:02.933
NEXT TIME, LISTEN.

41:04.333 --> 41:07.500
* FEELS SO FREE,
DON'T NEED ANYONE TO KEEP *

41:07.500 --> 41:11.300
* MY MIND, MY BODY, MY SOUL *

41:11.300 --> 41:15.300
* SINGLE *

41:15.300 --> 41:19.233
* LADIES *
